026. שני רעולי פנים פרצו לעסק וירו לעברו מטווח קצר. מחמוד היה ידוע בקהילה בזכות מעורבותו החברתית ועזרתו לנזקקים, כולל תספורות חינם לקשישים ולמשפחות מעוטות יכולת.","case_narrative_en":"Mahmoud Gaawi, 25, was shot and killed inside his barbershop in Kafr Qara on the evening of January 5, 2026. Two masked individuals reportedly broke into the business and shot him at close range. Mahmoud was known in the community for his good reputation and charitable initiatives, including offering free haircuts to the elderly and needy families.","review_status":"flagged_for_review","pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2026-01-01_2026-05-15","enrichment_passes":0,"_pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2026-01-01_2026-05-15","run_id":"canonical","case_index":100}